Sec. 3. Be it further resolved, That, the President of Texas is hereby requested immediately to furnish the Govern-
ment of the United States, through their accredited Minister near this Government, with a copy of this Joint Resolution;
Laws of the Republic of Texas.also to furnish the Convention to assemble at Austin, on the fourth of July next, a copy of the same—And the same shall take effect from and after its passage.
